
# ─── OBSERVABILITY ────────────────────────────────────────
# Sentry (or self-hosted Glitchtip) for error tracking.
# 1. pnpm add @sentry/node --filter @worldpulse/api
# 2. Set your DSN below
# SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@sentry.io/123
# SENTRY_TRACES_SAMPLE_RATE=0.1

# OpenTelemetry traces from scraper pipeline are emitted as structured pino logs.
# Integrate with Grafana Loki / Datadog / OpenSearch for trace correlation.
# To upgrade to real OTel SDK: pnpm add @opentelemetry/api @opentelemetry/sdk-trace-node --filter @worldpulse/scraper
